member.name: T:HarmonyOfEmotions.ServiceDefaults.Utils.Spectrogram.SpectrogramGenerator
member.summary: Instantiate a spectrogram generator. This module calculates the FFT over a moving window as data comes in. Using the Add() method to load new data and process it as it arrives.
member.param: Number of samples to use for each FFT operation. This value must be a power of 2.
Number of samples to step forward
Frequency data lower than this value (Hz) will not be stored
Frequency data higher than this value (Hz) will not be stored
This value will be added to displayed frequency axis tick labels
